7, major importing countries recorded the following import prices: in Belgium ($6.1 per kg) and Italy ($5.9 per kg), while France ($4.8 per kg) and the UK ($5.5 per kg) were amongst the lowest.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">From 2007 to 2017, the most notable rate of growth in terms of import prices was attained by the Netherlands (+1.8% per year), while the other leaders experienced more modest paces of growth.</p>\r\n<p>Source: <a href=\"https://www.indexbox.io/store/eu-cocoa-butter-market-report-analysis-and-forecast-to-2020/\" target=\"_blank\"></a></p>', 61, '2019-07-18 22:44:15', 0),
