(77, 'Aluminum Sheet, Plate, And Foil Market in the USA - Key Insights', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img title=\"Aluminum Sheet, Plate, And Foil Market in the USA - Key Insights\" alt=\"Aluminum Sheet, Plate, And Foil Market in the USA - Key Insights\" height=\"420\" width=\"722\" src=\"https://www.indexbox.io/published/publicdata/U983154/attachments/SC/products_covers_overlays/331315.jpg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p>IndexBox has just published a new report, <a href=\"https://www.indexbox.io/store/us-aluminum-sheet-plate-and-foil-market-analysis-and-forecast-to-2020/\">the U.S. Aluminum Sheet, Plate, And Foil Market. Analysis And Forecast to 2025</a>. Here is a summary of the report\'s key findings.</p><p></p><p>The revenue of the market of aluminum sheets, plates, and foil in the U.S. amounted to $10.2B in 2018, growing by 12% against the previous year. This figure reflects the total revenues of producers and importers (excluding logistics costs, retail marketing costs, and retailers\' margins, which will be included in the final consumer price). The market value increased at an average annual rate of +3.2% over the period from 2013 to 2018; the trend pattern remained relatively stable, with somewhat noticeable fluctuations in certain years. The pace of growth appeared the most rapid in 2017, when it surged by 15% against the previous year. Over the period under review, the market for aluminum sheet, plate, and foil reached its maximum level in 2018, and is expected to retain its growth in the near future. </p><b>Production of Aluminum Sheets, Plates, And Foil in the USA</b><br /><br /><p>In value terms, production of aluminum sheets, plates, and foil totaled $13.8B in 2018. Overall, production of aluminum sheets, plates, and foil continues to indicate a pronounced drop. The pace of growth was the most pronounced in 2014, when the the output figure increased by 2.1% y-o-y. In that year, production of aluminum sheets, plates, and foil attained i